<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Morning View Drive | Playbill</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@400;600&family=Libre+Baskerville:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

body {
  margin: 0;
  background: #ffffff;
  color: #000;
  font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif;
}

/* PLAYBILL HEADER */
.playbill-header {
  background: #ffcc00;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 25px 10px 15px;
  border-bottom: 4px solid black;
}

.playbill-header h1 {
  font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
  font-size: 3.5em;
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  margin: 0;
}

.subhead {
  font-size: 0.9em;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  margin-top: 5px;
}

/* TITLE SECTION */
.title-section {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px 20px 10px;
}

.title-section h2 {
  font-size: 2.5em;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.title-section p {
  margin: 5px 0;
}

/* CONTENT */
.container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: auto;
  padding: 20px;
}

.section {
  margin-top: 40px;
}

.section h3 {
  font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
  border-bottom: 2px solid black;
  padding-bottom: 5px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

/* CAST LIST */
.cast-list div {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  border-bottom: 1px dotted #999;
  padding: 6px 0;
}

/* CREDITS */
.credits p {
  margin: 6px 0;
}

/* FOOTER */
.footer {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 50px;
  padding: 30px 20px;
  border-top: 2px solid black;
  font-size: 0.9em;
}

.sponsor {
  font-weight: bold;
  margin-top: 10px;
}

/* SMALL CAPS LOOK */
.smallcaps {
  font-variant: small-caps;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="playbill-header">
  <h1>PLAYBILL</h1>
  <div class="subhead">Malibu Civic Theatre</div>
</div>

<div class="title-section">
  <h2>Morning View Drive</h2>
  <p class="smallcaps">Written by Kerry Knuppe</p>
  <p>A Staged Reading</p>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Logline</h3>
    <p>
      A deaf, blind 92-year-old and his wife (who battles Alzheimer's) must defend their home against a pair of burglars.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Synopsis</h3>
    <p>
      For seventy-five years, Ron and Julie Merrimen have lived on the once-rural coastline of Malibu. Now in their nineties, Ron is blind, hard of hearing, and confined to his wheelchair while Julie battles Alzheimer's.
    </p>
    <p>
      When two con men scheme to rob their home, Julie must become Ron's eyes, ears and physical capabilities — and Ron must become Julie's short-term memory.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Cast</h3>
    <div class="cast-list">
      <div><span>Paul Denk</span><span>—</span></div>
      <div><span>Lisa Robins</span><span>—</span></div>
      <div><span>Peter Gregory</span><span>—</span></div>
      <div><span>James Morris</span><span>—</span></div>
      <div><span>Johnny Cendejas</span><span>—</span></div>
      <div><span>Austin Basis</span><span>—</span></div>
      <div><span>Mitch Levene</span><span>—</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section credits">
    <h3>Creative Team</h3>
    <p><strong>Director:</strong> Sarah Gurfield</p>
    <p><strong>Producer:</strong> Ivan Rivas</p>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="footer">
  <p class="smallcaps">Sponsored by the City of Malibu</p>
  <p>Malibu Civic Theatre</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
